caption.title: Prevalence of syndemic factors by childhood sexual abuse among the sample of black MSM ( N = 1,002).
caption.p: (A) HIV-positive. (B) HIV-unknown. (C) Number of male sexual partners in past 90 days. (D) Number of acts of CAI in past 90 days. (E) Engaged in binge drinking in past 90 days. (F) Engaged in illicit use of substances in the past 90 days. (G) Experienced IPV in past 30 days.
